  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain the phenomenon of total internal reflection</item>
<item>Describe the workings and uses of optical fibers</item>
<item>Analyze the reason for the sparkle of diamonds</item>
</list></md:abstract>
